To build the real firmware:
1. Open the esp32-firmware project in VS Code with ESP-IDF extension
2. Set the device type in sdkconfig: CONFIG_YKP_DEVICE_TYPE_MOTOR=y
3. Run: idf.py build
4. Find the binary at: build/ykp_motor.bin
5. Copy it here and rename to ykp_motor_v1.1.2.bin
